:::...> About

Star Defender 3 Game  is the explosive sequel to Star Defender 2, but with better stuff stolen from the Insectus.

The Star Defender 3 game is finally here! Get ready to fight through hoards of Insectus aliens as they mercilessly attack the Earth in Star Defender3! Star Defender3 lets you blast through 8 huge missions as you prove who's boss, once and for all!

:::...> Features
:
Star Defender 3 has 100 levels and fantastic new weapons made with stolen Insectus technology. Star Defender 3 has a new progressive system of bonuses. The brilliant new Star Defender 3 locations make this the most exciting Star Defender yet!

The explosions in the new Star Defender3 will blow you away, so suit up as a Star Defender Novice or Veteran, fire up your laser and get to work blasting alien hoards!
